40 or mental health treatment provider who is (1) an employee of the principal's attending physician
41 or mental health treatment provider, (2) an employee of the health facility in which the principal
42 is a patient, or (3) an employee of a nursing home or any adult care home where the principal
43 resides. I further state that I do not have any claim against the principal or the estate of the
44 principal.
