37 public are present to watch you sign it. You then should consider giving a copy to your primary
38 physician and a trusted relative, and should consider filing it with the Advanced Health Care
39 Directive Registry maintained by the North Carolina Secretary of State:
40 http://www.nclifelinks.org/ahcdr/State.
